hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: We'd like to invite you for an interview cheap buy online magnum blood flow For the next 30 minutes, I received an online seminar in modern feminist dialectic, intersectionalism (don’t look it up, it’ll do your head in) and the most terrible of crimes – “internalising patriarchy”. With all due respect, the only time I ever got close to internalising patriarchy was a phase. Despite my love of Liza Minnelli, I realised it’s not the lifestyle for me. You can probably add homophobic to my list of crimes now.
